casebody.data:
STATE
v.
WELCH, Donald Arthur A158592(S065861) Supreme Court of Oregon. June 7, 2018

Petitioner on review's petition for review is allowed. The decision of the Court of Appeals is vacated, and this ease is remanded to the Court of Appeals for reconsideration in light of State v. K. J. B., 362 Or. 777, 416 P.3d 291 (2018).

Review Allowed.
